abstract: Michele Bachmann says she raised about $4 million in the last quarter, a sign that her campaign is still having trouble attracting big donors.
snippet: Michele Bachmann says she raised about $4 million in the last quarter, a sign that her campaign is still having trouble attracting big donors.
lead_paragraph: ROCK RAPIDS, Iowa -- Although candidates are not required to report their fund-raising and expenses for the financial quarter ending Sept. 30 until Saturday, Representative Michele Bachmann offered a peek here Friday into the top-line number she would report.
